<h1 class="no_toc fs-9" id="context">Context</h1>

<p class="fs-6 fw-300">When we talk to a person face to face, content is often put into context. In this way misunderstandings can be avoided. The same is applicable to content on the web. If the context is not given, users cannot classify the meaning of individual elements.</p>

<hr />

